main event: An unidentified flying object was sighted near Eglin AFB, Florida, which was later determined to be a meteorite.
interesting points: The sighting involved a ground observer who reported a white streak or trail composed of discernible particles,The pilot described a blinking blue light with a green trail,The object was visible for approximately half an hour and appeared to move at a tremendous rate of speed,It came to a virtual standstill before accelerating again,The visibility conditions were clear, and the object was thought to be under intelligent control.
sighted object: white streak or trail; blinking blue light with green trailing
witness description: Electrical engineer, 35 years old, Stockton, California
